Hold up, that amber necklace.[p]
Isn't that the exorcist girl? The sole survivor of the massacre? What is she doing here?[p]
She's whistling? She's telling me to come? [p]
Hah! Who does she think i am? [p]
As if anyone would trust a girl whose family they just murdered[p]
[_tb_end_text]

[bg  time="1000"  method="crossfade"  storage="sequences/Kai_memory_7.png"  ]
