At that point i didn't trust you, not one bit. [p]
But i could read it in your eyes that you didn't come to bring me harm. Therefore, out of curiosity, i flied toward you. [p]
From that we stayed together. [p]
You took care of me and healed my wounds. [p]
Deep down i knew you were just seeking a chance to evenge your family. [p]
And yet all that time, your eyes when taking care of me didn't show a single hint of fakeness.[p]
[_tb_end_text]

